article_title: AOL Results Top Expectations on Advertising Strength
article_text:
AOL Inc. reported a slight dip in earnings during the first quarter of the year, though the company logged better-than-expected 7.2% revenue growth amid stronger advertising.

Shares gained 1.6% in premarket trading.

AOL has invested heavily in advertising technology over the past several years, creating a bright spot for the company as it...
